v></span></span></span>Test automation can be a game-changer for software p=
rojects, but only if done right. Too often, teams either overcomplicate it =
or avoid it altogether. To help you navigate the pitfalls and get the most =
out of test automation, here are five rules that can set you up for success=
.</p><h2 id=3D"a2fc" class=3D"xg xh st bb xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr xs =
xt xu xv xw xx xy xz ya yb yc yd bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">#1: Jus=
t Start Doing It</h2><p id=3D"5307" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj s=
t wk b wl ye wn wo wp yf wr ws wt yg wv ww wx yh wz xa xb yi xd xe xf fi bg=
" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">The biggest mistake you can make with test=
 automation? Overthinking it. Just start.</p><p id=3D"f78a" class=3D"pw-pos=
t-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz=
 xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Too many teams spe=
nd months trying to define the =E2=80=9Cperfect=E2=80=9D automation strateg=
y or toolset. They get stuck in research mode, afraid to take action. But a=
utomation is something you learn by doing. You=E2=80=99ll write some bad te=
sts. Some will be flaky. Some will be pointless. That=E2=80=99s part of the=
 process.</p><p id=3D"328f" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b w=
l wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" data-s=
electable-paragraph=3D"">Start small. Automate basic regression tests or cr=
itical user flows first. Learn from failures, iterate, and improve. The soo=
ner you start, the sooner you=E2=80=99ll build expertise and confidence.</p=
><h2 id=3D"bbaa" class=3D"xg xh st bb xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr xs xt x=
u xv xw xx xy xz ya yb yc yd bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">#2: Do Not =
Try to Automate Everything</h2><p id=3D"ac8e" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragra=
ph wi wj st wk b wl ye wn wo wp yf wr ws wt yg wv ww wx yh wz xa xb yi xd x=
e xf fi bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Not everything is worth automati=
ng. Some things <em class=3D"yj">shouldn=E2=80=99t</em> be automated at all=
.</p><p id=3D"4d5c" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn =
wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" data-selectabl=
e-paragraph=3D"">Examples of bad automation candidates:</p><ul class=3D""><=
li id=3D"bd23" class=3D"wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww w=
x wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf pd yk yl bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Featu=
res that are still unstable or frequently changing (your test maintenance e=
ffort will be painful).</li><li id=3D"6f29" class=3D"wi wj st wk b wl ym wn=
 wo wp yn wr ws wt yo wv ww wx yp wz xa xb yq xd xe xf pd yk yl bg" data-se=
lectable-paragraph=3D"">UI elements with constantly shifting designs (you=
=E2=80=99ll chase moving selectors all day).</li><li id=3D"6724" class=3D"w=
i wj st wk b wl ym wn wo wp yn wr ws wt yo wv ww wx yp wz xa xb yq xd xe xf=
 pd yk yl bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Extremely complex scenarios th=
at require too much test setup.</li></ul><p id=3D"1d65" class=3D"pw-post-bo=
dy-paragraph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa =
xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Instead, focus on test=
