ble-paragraph=3D"">Repetitive regression tests that run often.</li><li id=
=3D"efac" class=3D"wi wj st wk b wl ym wn wo wp yn wr ws wt yo wv ww wx yp =
wz xa xb yq xd xe xf pd yk yl bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">APIs and b=
ackend logic (they=E2=80=99re usually more stable than UI tests).</li></ul>=
<p id=3D"d4b1" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp=
 wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" data-selectable-par=
agraph=3D"">Be smart about where you invest your automation efforts.</p><h2=
 id=3D"32b3" class=3D"xg xh st bb xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr xs xt xu xv=
 xw xx xy xz ya yb yc yd bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">#3: Never Delet=
e a Test</h2><p id=3D"1f1f" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b w=
l ye wn wo wp yf wr ws wt yg wv ww wx yh wz xa xb yi xd xe xf fi bg" data-s=
electable-paragraph=3D"">Every test you write contributes to your functiona=
l coverage. If a test starts failing, don=E2=80=99t just delete it =E2=80=
=94 ask why.</p><p id=3D"993b" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk =
b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" dat=
a-selectable-paragraph=3D"">If the feature is deprecated, sure, remove the =
test. But if it=E2=80=99s failing due to a real issue, it=E2=80=99s an oppo=
rtunity to improve your app.</p><p id=3D"6b54" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragr=
aph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd =
xe xf fi bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Good tests act as safety nets, =
catching regressions early. Even old tests might surface unexpected bugs in=
 the future. Instead of deleting them, consider:</p><ul class=3D""><li id=
=3D"4c11" class=3D"wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy =
wz xa xb xc xd xe xf pd yk yl bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Refactorin=
g flaky tests.</li><li id=3D"3e1b" class=3D"wi wj st wk b wl ym wn wo wp yn=
 wr ws wt yo wv ww wx yp wz xa xb yq xd xe xf pd yk yl bg" data-selectable-=
paragraph=3D"">Marking some as =E2=80=9Cskipped=E2=80=9D until they can be =
