h=3D"">Moving lower-priority tests to a separate suite that runs less frequ=
ently.</li></ul><p id=3D"f2da" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk =
b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt wu wv ww wx wy wz xa xb xc xd xe xf fi bg" dat=
a-selectable-paragraph=3D"">Your tests are valuable assets. Treat them like=
 it.</p><h2 id=3D"77f0" class=3D"xg xh st bb xi xj xk xl xm xn xo xp xq xr =
xs xt xu xv xw xx xy xz ya yb yc yd bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">#4: =
