 wi wj st wk b wl ye wn wo wp yf wr ws wt yg wv ww wx yh wz xa xb yi xd xe =
xf fi bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"">UI test flakiness is often caused =
by unstable element selectors. If your tests constantly break because eleme=
nts can=E2=80=99t be found, you=E2=80=99re doing it wrong.</p><p id=3D"5113=
" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph wi wj st wk b wl wm wn wo wp wq wr ws wt =
